MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 364c2b772391e46dba637935c558b9b2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Wyvern
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::MythSO
  pageNumber: 37
  mythName: Wyvern
  omens:
  - '1. Crowned stag, crawling, poisoned. Its

    antlers are known to burn scaled
    beasts.'
  - '2. A burial mound surrounded by a low stone

    wall. Much of it has been dug
    up, petty

    treasures scattered. The Wyvern

    screeches in the distance.'
  - '3. The bloated body of a poisoned Knight,

    adoring Squire weeping at their
    side.'
  - '4. Two foul eggs laid among battle carrion.

    The air feels sour. The poisonous
    young

    hatch at dark, share a feast, then lurch in

    opposite directions.
    A serrated blade

    forged with pain (2d6) lies with the dead.'
  - '5. The Wyvern soars low, seeking revenge

    for a failed attack on its nest.
    The

    attackers have already fled. It clutches

    one of their silver shields
    (d6, A1), blessed

    by the iron willow.'
  - '6. Fearing for its nest, the Wyvern lands to

    fight. If the situation is
    hopeless it flies to

    a neighbouring Realm, plotting revenge.'
  verse: 'All jack-a-jaw and neck a knot''d string

    All fess-a-wing and tail
    a bane''d sting'
  castEntries:
  - name: The Wyvern, That Foul Twisted Reptile
    statBlock: 'VIG 17, CLA 17, SPI 5, 12 GD

      A2 in flight, A4 on ground (cowering
      wings)'
    notes: 'Bite & throw (3d10, slow when grounded) or

      sting (d10, wound causes
      bloating death

      within an hour unless thoroughly washed

      out with
      fresh milk)

      Disgusted by the sound of a baby''s cry.

      Fast but
      clumsy flyer.'
  - name: Its Poisonous Young
    statBlock: 'VIG 5, CLA 10, SPI 2, 3 GD

      A1 (cold hide)'
    notes: Thrash (d8, carries its mother's poison)
  flavorTable:
    title: THE POISONOUS YOUNG
    columns:
    - header: Form
      values:
      - Adder
      - Newt
      - Frog
      - Weasel
      - Scorpion
      - Swan
    - header: Abomination
      values:
      - Barbed scales
      - Unhinged jaw
      - Prehensile tongue
      - Bloated stomach
      - Twin tails
      - Horned snout
  visibleByDefault: 0
  visibleMarkerPrefab: {fileID: 0}
